@{b}Registration@{ub}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

@{b}Why register?@{ub}
@{b}VideoArchiv@{ub} is  Shareware. When  registered you  will  receive  a personal
password, which will enable the disabled  functions of the programme. This
will also stop those nasty requesters, which appear to ask you to register
when the programme is used frequently.

Once registered, you will not need to  register each time a new version of
@{b}VideoArchiv@{ub} is  released. You  will be able  to use your password with any
future releases. If this is not the case, you will, at least, be offered a
very special update price.

@{b}How to register?@{ub}
Registration is  very simple. Please use  the included @{"registration form" link "Registration_e.txt/main" 0},
fill in the gaps, print, then send the form and money to the address shown
above. Once received, your personal password will be  sent either by post,
or EMail (please choose).

Thank you very much!

